name: Expanding Reality
description: Expanding Reality is the final variation of the ‘Mutating Reality’ series. This piece can only be acquired if you own all four previous OBJKTS [91000, 92805, 94241, 101061]. Once you own all four, this piece will be dropped into your wallet. ‘Expanding Reality’ will only be available for purchase through the secondary market, if those who own it choose to list it for sale. I am distributing 1 edition per person.
